LEXICON Determiners

!! Determiners: Possessives

! mo/do etc have no independent existance, therefore they are possessive determiners not possessive pronouns.
mo+Det+Poss+1P+Sg:mo		#;	! my
!mo+Det+Poss+1P+Sg+NG:m'		#;	! my
mo+Det+Poss+1P+Sg+Short:m'		#;	! my  - changed +NG to +Short (as per Trond) for m' before a vowel
do+Det+Poss+2P+Sg:do		#;	! your
!do+Det+Poss+2P+Sg+NG:d'		#;	! your
do+Det+Poss+2+Sg+Short:d'		#;	! your - changed +NG to +Short (as per Trond for m' for d' before a vowel
do+Det+Poss+2P+Sg+NG:t'		#;	! your Bardic Apr 2019
do+Det+Poss+2P+Sg+NG:th'		#;	! your Bardic Apr 2019
ár+Det+Poss+1P+Pl:ár			#;	! our
bhur+Det+Poss+2P+Pl:bhur	#;	! your 

! this information is on the noun as initial mutation
! use corresponding +Len / +Ecl to determine whether sing/pl, masc/fem
a+Det+Poss+3P:a			#;	! her/his/their
! a+Det+Poss+3P+Pl:a		#;	! their
! a+Det+Poss+3P+Sg+Fem:a		#;	! her
! a+Det+Poss+3P+Sg+Masc:a		#;	! his

! SEE PRON-LEX á+Det+Poss+3P:á		#;	! it: bhí sé á dhíol  (being sold?)
!á+Det+Poss+3P+Sg+Fem:á		#;	! it: bhí sé á dhíol aici (she was selling it)
!á+Det+Poss+3P+Sg+Masc:á		#;	! it: bhí sé á dhíol aige (he was selling it)
!á+Det+Poss+3P+Pl:á			#;	! it: bhí sé á dhíol acu  (they were selling it)


